# Online Educational Platform — System Analysis

System requirements analysis and workflow design for a comprehensive online tutoring platform supporting curriculum-based lessons, live sessions, financial settlement, and multi-role management.

---

## 🎯 Platform Overview

A web-based educational platform for individual and group tutoring sessions aligned with the Egyptian national curriculum — supporting all subjects and grade levels.

---

## 👥 Roles & Actors

| Role | Responsibilities |
|------|----------------|
| Teacher | Upload content, manage schedule, conduct sessions, submit reports |
| Student | Browse & purchase lessons, attend sessions, submit questions |
| Parent/Guardian | Manage wallet, track child's progress |
| Supervisor | Manage platform operations, assign session links, resolve issues |
| Technical Support | Assist teachers and students with platform usage |
| Admin | Full platform control and financial oversight |

---

## 📚 Core Modules

### 1. Content Management
- Lesson plans, quizzes, assignments, and PDF materials
- Content visible only to students who purchased the lesson
- Teacher profile with credentials and experience

### 2. Session Management
```plantuml
@startuml Session_Flow

|Supervisor|
start
:Review teacher schedule;
:Create meeting link;
:Assign to session slot;

|Teacher|
:Start session from platform;
:System records attendance automatically;
:Submit post-session report;
(content covered + attendance);

|System|
:Calculate session cost;
:Debit student wallet;
:Credit teacher balance;

stop
@enduml
```

### 3. Financial Settlement

| Model | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| Per-session fee | Fixed cost per lesson duration |
| Cashback points | Wallet points redeemable for lessons |
| Online payment | Payment gateway integration |

### 4. Communication
- Chat rooms per teacher-student group
- Supervisor can join any chat room
- Blog / Q&A section for curriculum questions
- Educational articles by platform team

---

## 🔐 Access Control

| Content Type | Access |
|-------------|--------|
| Lesson materials (PDF, quizzes) | Purchased students only |
| Session link | Registered & paid students only |
| Blog / Q&A | All users |
| Teacher profile | Public |

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Systems Analysis (SRS / BRD)
- PlantUML — Workflow diagrams
- Mermaid — Sequence diagrams

